{"thag2.41:0.1":"Theragatha 2.41 ","thag2.41:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.41:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.41:0.4":"Kumarakassapattheragatha ","thag2.41:1.1":"“Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","thag2.41:1.2":"aho no satthu sampada; ","thag2.41:1.3":"Yattha etadisam dhammam, ","thag2.41:1.4":"savako sacchikahiti. ","thag2.41:2.1":"Asankheyyesu kappesu, ","thag2.41:2.2":"sakkayadhigata ahu; ","thag2.41:2.3":"Tesamayam pacchimako, ","thag2.41:2.4":"carimoyam samussayo; ","thag2.41:2.5":"Jatimaranasamsaro, ","thag2.41:2.6":"natthi dani punabbhavo”ti. ","thag2.41:2.7":"… Kumarakassapo thero …. "}